A man has been killed and one injured after a three vehicle collision on the R21 in Centurion near the Nellmapius turn off on Wednesday.The vehicle collision was between a large truck,bakkie and light motor vehicle.According to paramedics, the bakkie and truck were found on the side of the road where as the light vehicle was found in the middle of the isle.Emergency services found one of the patients trapped inside the bakkie and had already died when paramedics attended to him.&#8220;Paramedics found the body of a man lying trapped inside of the bakkie. Unfortunately, the man had already succumbed to his multiple, fatal injuries, Nothing could be done for him and he was declared dead on the scene,&#8221; ER24 said in statement.The other patient sustained multiple injuries and was transported to the nearest hospital.Meanwhile police are still investigating the cause of the collision.